Z","msg":"小弟一兩個月前開始玩twitter，得閒reply下啲多人follow嘅政要同記者，retweet with comment一啲對外國人嚟講有興趣嘅新聞<br />\n<br />\n啱啱集會完返緊屋企就收到個德州人嘅PM<br />\n佢讚賞香港人嘅勇氣，為咗唔會令自己忘記我哋呢班勇敢抗爭嘅人，佢紋咗個紫荊花喺手（仲要係first hand tattoo！）<br />\n佢話佢係火箭球迷（佢同時附上咗佢左手前臂有Harden紋身短片），但對於球會回應好失望，希望入場高舉紫荊花紋身，即使要被驅趕出場，都要作出致敬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nF1A0ft.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnF1A0ft.png&h=85d77121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxuSh18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxuSh18.png&h=36b24a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4wM6Vu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4wM6Vu.png&h=29f92573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家請入去呢個tweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LMangonada/status/1182465633444859904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLMangonada%2Fstatus%2F1182465633444859904&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm97M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=c338a682\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLMangonada%2Fstatus%2F1182465633444859904&h=2483c2f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LMangonada/status/1182465633444859904</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Like, reply, retweet, and follow.<br />\n唔好辜負嚟自德州嘅支持！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:15:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">推</span><br />\n- <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母 今晚儲夠人 今日美國傾 <br />\n但twitter 熱門一個香港都冇 </span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部人：國際線啊！！！！幾個製出個tweet 有幾難啊<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654565\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654565</a> </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討